Black First Land First (BLF) will ask the Office of the Public Protector to give an update and process to get back the R26 billion stolen by, amongst others, ABSA and Johann Rupert from the South African Reserve Bank. The Zoom meeting with the Office of the Public Protector will be held under the following details: 1. Date: 20 April 2021
2. Time: 10:30 BLF shall have a Zoom media briefing after the meeting with the Public Protector around 12:00 The Zoom meeting details will follow for the media briefing. Issued by Black First Land First, National Coordinating Committee (BLF NCC)
